  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was-- this-- this sergeant, his name was Szacserovszki.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The reason why I remember his name, he was a very-- a very decent guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, a few months later, he deserted to the partisans, because we saw him later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- he disappeared from us altogether.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, OK, I'm going to keep him here in the kitchen to-- to-- to peel-- to peel potatoes, to help in the kitchen, because we have-- our group had a kitchen, a field kitchen, you know that was-- that were-- they-- they were cooking whatever-- whatever the rations, the rations, probably, [? and ?] we were getting.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the boys in the kitchen, they knew-- those were all our boys-- they knew how sick I was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just let me-- let me sit there and stay and-- and do-- do nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few days later, this doctor, again, asked this sergeant to-- in order for me to recuperate from that-- from that tudogyulladas, to get a little bit more rest, to assign me our [NON-ENGLISH]-- our group had six horses, three wagons, six horses.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To the-- to the-- to-- I got an assignment to-- to take care of the horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during the day, we didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the horses-- this was in the summer-- to take the horses out, out on a-- on a, you know, on the pasture.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So after a-- after a couple of weeks that I went through, I got back-- back to my-- my strength.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I was back-- it was back into the-- into-- into the regular group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then from there-- from there we were sent to Wlochy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Wlochy was on an outskirt-- outskirt of the city of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
